snippet.title: Anto Sharp
snippet.description:
Hey I’m Anto Sharp
A British Actor, Comedian and the creator of the ‘Straight in my Basket’ series. 
Ive been creating comedy content since 2015 on Facebook, Instagram and now TikTok.
Series such as Do You Hear Me, How to survive an apocalypse, The Covid Vaccine Skits and Half top duets like the Nail Technician, Teaching Pottery and loads more.

You'll find all of my Comedy content here in Comedy Shorts and weekly Compilations, Fun stuff with the kids and me and my wife Jen, trying some ridiculous trends.

If you enjoy your stay be sure to hit Subscribe.
